Package org.sbml.jsbml.ext.fbc

Class LogicalOperator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.AbstractTreeNode
      • org.sbml.jsbml.AbstractSBase
        • org.sbml.jsbml.ext.fbc.LogicalOperator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode, Association, SBase, TreeNodeWithChangeSupport
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    And, Or

    public abstract class LogicalOperator
extends AbstractSBase
implements Association
    Represents a collection of genes in a logical expression.

    Is is only ever instantiated as one of its subclasses: And and Or.

    Since:
    1.1
    Author:
    Andreas Dräger
